  "title": "12 Months Project Coordinator (Quality & Change Management)  #NJN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Yio Chu Kang</strong><br /><strong>12 Months Contract</strong><br /><strong>8.45am to 6.15pm (Mon to Fri)</strong></p><ul><li>Attached to IT Project Team</li><li>Project Governance – participate in project as QM rep to ensure project team adheres to the SDLC guidelines and deliverables, provides guidance from governance standpoint, conduct Change Review Meeting or Change Review Assessment to ensure readiness prior implementation and subsequent follow up post implementation activities.</li><li>Change Management – consolidate all Change Requests for Change Advisory Board review, ensures all deliverables in place and facilitate the CAB review session. Provide oversight on the deliverables submission to ensure all requirements met prior approval for implementation.</li><li>There will be other functions such as administering and conduct of periodic user access matrix and user access</li></ul><p><br />Jessica Nguyen Huynh Thanh Truc</p><p>CEI Reg. No. R23113787</p><p>EA License No. 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p></p>",
